description:
&quot;What would you do if I told you I always wanted to be alone with you...?&quot; 

&quot;We've been friends forever!&quot; 

Me, Aki and Tetsuji have been friends since we were kids. We all love games and we're always together. But everything changed once we got to experience a game called &quot;Real Game&quot;... with a love setting, nonetheless! Tetsuji and Aki ignored my questions completely and just went ahead, making me the main character of the game. Kissing in secret, getting teased in a closet...! This is a virtual love game that seems too real, played by three guys and I'm the only one reacting!
